    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the control that blocks sleep. The script targets the habit of monitoring, managing, and willing yourself toward sleep — the effort that keeps it at a distance."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I keep trying to manage my way to sleep, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I'm watching myself for signs of tiredness and it's keeping me awake, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I don't know how to stop trying, I am open to letting sleep happen without my help." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I keep trying to force it." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm monitoring myself for tiredness." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I keep checking the clock." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm calculating how many hours I have left." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " The harder I try the further away it gets." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I don't know how to hand over control." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm exhausted from trying to sleep." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I am ready to stop trying and let it happen." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Sleep doesn't need my effort." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I give my body permission to do this without my guidance." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I stop checking the clock." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " The hours take care of themselves." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I release my grip on the night." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Sleep arrives without my help." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I rest even when sleep hasn't arrived yet." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I let go and allow." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times." }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 4 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Let go of control.\" The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
